race.description: Sportsbet Bet With Mates Maiden Plate
race.comment: YOU'RESOGOLDEN (12) gave supporters a bold sight on debut at Strathalbyn, only grabbed late after doing plenty of work. With natural improvement and another favourable draw, she'll take plenty of running down. TIDDY WIDDY (10) has the fitness edge and continues to race honestly despite the maiden proving elusive. Maps to blend in nicely from the middle alley and can give this another solid shake. ELEGANT LILLY (11) resumes for the Oxlade team after contesting some strong maidens in her first prep. Her recent work suggests she's come back in great order and a bright return is on the cards. EVEN IN AMERICA (9) improved sharply second-up when ridden forward at Strathalbyn, only to be reeled in late. Freshened since and boosted by a sharp jumpout win, he's capable of playing a major role.
